name: Out Of Busines
description:
Out Of Business depicts an image of
banks in the future. It's a collection of
references to the crypto world with
callbacks to Cryptopunks, Bitcoin,
Beeple, Doge, Facebook, the death of
fiat, Elon Musk, and many more. The
collector of this piece will get an
aluminum physical print with a signed
and numbered certificate of
authenticity (1/1). Made in Adobe
Illustrator. 100% vector.
